{
  "video_id": "Qzmt2wQMhYo",
  "title": "What's your 200-year plan? | Raghava KK",
  "es": 1,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 0.0,
      "end_time": 7000.0,
      "text": "Translator: Joseph Geni Reviewer: Morton Bast"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 16346.0,
      "end_time": 18360.0,
      "text": "About 75 years ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 18360.0,
      "end_time": 20595.0,
      "text": "my grandfather, a young man,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 20595.0,
      "end_time": 22506.0,
      "text": "walked into a tent"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 22506.0,
      "end_time": 24300.0,
      "text": "that was converted into a"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 24300.0,
      "end_time": 25714.0,
      "text": "movie theater like that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 25714.0,
      "end_time": 27913.0,
      "text": "and he fell hopelessly in love"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 27914.0,
      "end_time": 29243.0,
      "text": "with the woman he saw on the"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 29243.0,
      "end_time": 32571.0,
      "text": "silver screen: none other than Mae West,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 32572.000000000004,
      "end_time": 34487.0,
      "text": "the heartthrob of the &#39;30s,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 34487.0,
      "end_time": 36527.0,
      "text": "and he could never forget her."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 36527.0,
      "end_time": 38447.0,
      "text": "In fact, when he had his daughter"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 38447.0,
      "end_time": 40639.0,
      "text": "many years later, he wanted to"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 40639.0,
      "end_time": 42550.0,
      "text": "name her after Mae West,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 42550.0,
      "end_time": 43639.0,
      "text": "but can you imagine an Indian"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 43639.0,
      "end_time": 45175.0,
      "text": "child name Mae West?"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 45175.0,
      "end_time": 46861.0,
      "text": "The Indian family said, no way!"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 46861.0,
      "end_time": 49799.0,
      "text": "So when my twin brother Kaesava"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 49799.0,
      "end_time": 52309.0,
      "text": "was born, he decided to tinker"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 52309.0,
      "end_time": 54240.0,
      "text": "with the spelling of Keshava&#39;s name."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 54240.0,
      "end_time": 57735.0,
      "text": "He said, if Mae West can be M-A-E,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 57735.0,
      "end_time": 61271.0,
      "text": "why can&#39;t Keshava be K-A-E?"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 61271.0,
      "end_time": 63511.0,
      "text": "So he changed Kaesava&#39;s spelling."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 63511.0,
      "end_time": 65582.0,
      "text": "Now Kaesava had a baby boy"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 65582.0,
      "end_time": 67782.0,
      "text": "called Rehan a couple of weeks ago."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 67782.0,
      "end_time": 70120.0,
      "text": "He decided to spell, or, rather,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 70130.0,
      "end_time": 72930.0,
      "text": "misspell Raehan with an A-E."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 72930.0,
      "end_time": 74228.0,
      "text": "You know, my grandfather died"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 74228.0,
      "end_time": 75588.0,
      "text": "many years ago when I was"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 75588.0,
      "end_time": 77428.0,
      "text": "little, but his love for Mae"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 77429.0,
      "end_time": 79900.0,
      "text": "West lives on as a misspelling"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 79900.0,
      "end_time": 81676.0,
      "text": "in the DNA of his progeny."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 81676.0,
      "end_time": 84820.0,
      "text": "That for me is successful legacy. (Laughs)"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 84820.0,
      "end_time": 86461.0,
      "text": "You know, as for me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 86462.0,
      "end_time": 87689.0,
      "text": "my wife and I have our own"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 87689.0,
      "end_time": 89297.0,
      "text": "crazy legacy project."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 89297.0,
      "end_time": 91489.0,
      "text": "We actually sit every few years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 91489.0,
      "end_time": 93862.0,
      "text": "argue, disagree, fight,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 93862.0,
      "end_time": 95704.0,
      "text": "and actually come up with our"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 95704.0,
      "end_time": 97720.0,
      "text": "very own 200-year plan."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 97720.0,
      "end_time": 99679.0,
      "text": "Our friends think we&#39;re mad."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 99680.0,
      "end_time": 101168.0,
      "text": "Our parents think we&#39;re cuckoo."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 101168.0,
      "end_time": 102504.0,
      "text": "Because, you know, we both"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 102504.0,
      "end_time": 103872.0,
      "text": "come from families that really"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 103872.0,
      "end_time": 106873.0,
      "text": "look up to humility and wisdom,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 106873.0,
      "end_time": 108504.0,
      "text": "but we both like to live"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 108504.0,
      "end_time": 109841.0,
      "text": "larger than life."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 109841.0,
      "end_time": 111351.0,
      "text": "I believe in the concept of"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 111351.0,
      "end_time": 114112.0,
      "text": "a Raja Yogi: Be a dude before"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 114112.0,
      "end_time": 115425.0,
      "text": "you can become an ascetic."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 115425.0,
      "end_time": 116920.0,
      "text": "This is me being a rock star,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 116920.0,
      "end_time": 118544.0,
      "text": "even if it&#39;s in my own house."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 118544.0,
      "end_time": 119808.0,
      "text": "You know?"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 119808.0,
      "end_time": 121520.0,
      "text": "So when Netra and I sat down"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 121520.0,
      "end_time": 122976.0,
      "text": "to make our first plan"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 122976.0,
      "end_time": 124960.0,
      "text": "10 years ago, we said"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 124960.0,
      "end_time": 127640.0,
      "text": "we want the focus of this plan"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 127640.0,
      "end_time": 128880.0,
      "text": "to go way beyond ourselves."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 128880.0,
      "end_time": 131543.0,
      "text": "What do we mean by beyond ourselves?"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 131544.0,
      "end_time": 134569.0,
      "text": "Well 200 years, we calculated,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 134569.0,
      "end_time": 136744.0,
      "text": "is at the end of our direct"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 136744.0,
      "end_time": 137912.0,
      "text": "contact with the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 137912.0,
      "end_time": 139271.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s nobody I&#39;ll meet in"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 139271.0,
      "end_time": 141583.0,
      "text": "my life will ever live beyond"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 141584.0,
      "end_time": 143488.0,
      "text": "200 years, so we thought"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 143488.0,
      "end_time": 144680.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s a perfect place where"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 144680.0,
      "end_time": 146592.0,
      "text": "we should situate our plan and"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 146592.0,
      "end_time": 148320.0,
      "text": "let our imagination take flight."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 148320.0,
      "end_time": 149864.0,
      "text": "You know, I never really"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 149864.0,
      "end_time": 151552.0,
      "text": "believed in legacy. What am I"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 151552.0,
      "end_time": 153543.0,
      "text": "going to leave behind? I&#39;m an artist."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 153544.0,
      "end_time": 156830.0,
      "text": "Until I made a cartoon about 9/11."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 156830.0,
      "end_time": 159478.0,
      "text": "It caused so much trouble for me."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 159478.0,
      "end_time": 160894.0,
      "text": "I was so upset."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 160894.0,
      "end_time": 163374.0,
      "text": "You know, a cartoon that was"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 163374.0,
      "end_time": 165370.0,
      "text": "meant to be a cartoon of the week"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 165380.0,
      "end_time": 168270.0,
      "text": "ended up staying so much longer."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 168270.0,
      "end_time": 170424.0,
      "text": "Now I&#39;m in the business of"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 170424.0,
      "end_time": 172101.0,
      "text": "creating art that will"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 172101.0,
      "end_time": 174464.0,
      "text": "definitely even outlive me, and"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 174464.0,
      "end_time": 176125.0,
      "text": "I think about what I want to"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 176125.0,
      "end_time": 178165.0,
      "text": "leave behind through those paintings."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 178165.0,
      "end_time": 180156.0,
      "text": "You know, the 9/11 cartoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 180157.0,
      "end_time": 183453.0,
      "text": "upset me so much that I decided"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 183453.0,
      "end_time": 184989.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ll never cartoon again."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 184989.0,
      "end_time": 186205.0,
      "text": "I said, I&#39;m never going to make any"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 186205.0,
      "end_time": 188118.0,
      "text": "honest public commentary again."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 188118.0,
      "end_time": 190613.0,
      "text": "But of course I continued"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 190613.0,
      "end_time": 192549.0,
      "text": "creating artwork that was honest"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 192549.0,
      "end_time": 194726.0,
      "text": "and raw, because I forgot about"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 194726.0,
      "end_time": 196944.0,
      "text": "how people reacted to my work."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 196944.0,
      "end_time": 198518.0,
      "text": "You know, sometimes forgetting"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 198518.0,
      "end_time": 201509.0,
      "text": "is so important to remain idealistic."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 201509.0,
      "end_time": 204245.0,
      "text": "Perhaps loss of memory is so"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 204246.0,
      "end_time": 206189.0,
      "text": "crucial for our survival"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 206189.0,
      "end_time": 207558.0,
      "text": "as human beings."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 207558.0,
      "end_time": 209412.0,
      "text": "One of the most important things"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 209413.0,
      "end_time": 211317.0,
      "text": "in my 200-year plan that Netra"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 211317.0,
      "end_time": 213703.0,
      "text": "and I write is what to forget"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 213703.0,
      "end_time": 215160.0,
      "text": "about ourselves."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 215160.0,
      "end_time": 216436.0,
      "text": "You know, we carry so much"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 216437.0,
      "end_time": 217846.0,
      "text": "baggage, from our parents,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 217846.0,
      "end_time": 219854.0,
      "text": "from our society, from so many"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 219854.0,
      "end_time": 223598.0,
      "text": "people -- fears, insecurities -- and"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 223598.0,
      "end_time": 225453.0,
      "text": "our 200-year plan really lists"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 225453.0,
      "end_time": 228505.0,
      "text": "all our childhood problems that we have to expire."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 228505.0,
      "end_time": 230600.0,
      "text": "We actually put an expiry date"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 230600.0,
      "end_time": 232480.0,
      "text": "on all our childhood problems."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 232480.0,
      "end_time": 234345.0,
      "text": "The latest date I put was,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 234345.0,
      "end_time": 237106.0,
      "text": "I said, I am going to expire"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 237106.0,
      "end_time": 239649.0,
      "text": "my fear of my leftist, feminist"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 239649.0,
      "end_time": 242580.0,
      "text": "mother-in-law, and this"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 242580.0,
      "end_time": 245180.0,
      "text": "today is the date! (Laughs)"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 245180.0,
      "end_time": 246771.0,
      "text": "She&#39;s watching. (Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 246771.0,
      "end_time": 251619.0,
      "text": "Anyway, you know, I really"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 251619.0,
      "end_time": 253619.0,
      "text": "make decisions all the time"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 253619.0,
      "end_time": 255204.0,
      "text": "about how I want to remember"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 255204.0,
      "end_time": 258476.0,
      "text": "myself, and that&#39;s the most important"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 258476.0,
      "end_time": 259995.0,
      "text": "kind of decisions I make."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 259995.0,
      "end_time": 261867.0,
      "text": "And this directly translates"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 261867.00000000003,
      "end_time": 263190.0,
      "text": "into my paintings."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 263190.0,
      "end_time": 265332.0,
      "text": "But like my friends, I can do"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 265332.0,
      "end_time": 266908.0,
      "text": "that really well on Facebook,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 266908.0,
      "end_time": 268827.0,
      "text": "Pinterest, Twitter, Flickr, YouTube."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 268827.0,
      "end_time": 270260.0,
      "text": "Name it, I&#39;m on it."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 270260.0,
      "end_time": 272339.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve started outsourcing my"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 272339.0,
      "end_time": 273932.0,
      "text": "memory to the digital world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 273932.0,
      "end_time": 275372.0,
      "text": "you know? But that comes"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 275372.0,
      "end_time": 276468.0,
      "text": "with a problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 276468.0,
      "end_time": 278990.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s so easy to think of"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 278990.0,
      "end_time": 279404.0,
      "text": "technology as a metaphor"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 279404.0,
      "end_time": 281750.0,
      "text": "for memory, but our brains"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 281750.0,
      "end_time": 283697.0,
      "text": "are not perfect storage devices"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 283697.0,
      "end_time": 284496.0,
      "text": "like technology."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 284496.0,
      "end_time": 286360.0,
      "text": "We only remember what we"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 286360.0,
      "end_time": 287291.0,
      "text": "want to. At least I do."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 287291.0,
      "end_time": 289794.0,
      "text": "And I rather think of our brains"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 289794.0,
      "end_time": 292193.0,
      "text": "as biased curators of our"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 292193.0,
      "end_time": 295320.0,
      "text": "memory, you know? And if"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 295330.0,
      "end_time": 296857.0,
      "text": "technology is not a metaphor for"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 296857.0,
      "end_time": 298489.0,
      "text": "memory, what is it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 298489.0,
      "end_time": 301505.0,
      "text": "Netra and I use our technology"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 301505.0,
      "end_time": 304730.0,
      "text": "as a tool in our 200-year plan"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 304730.0,
      "end_time": 307592.0,
      "text": "to really curate our digital legacy."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 307592.0,
      "end_time": 310609.0,
      "text": "That is a picture of my mother,"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 310609.0,
      "end_time": 313361.0,
      "text": "and she recently got a Facebook account."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 313362.0,
      "end_time": 315128.0,
      "text": "You know where this is going."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 315128.0,
      "end_time": 316962.0,
      "text": "And I&#39;ve been very supportive"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 316962.0,
      "end_time": 319344.0,
      "text": "until this picture shows up"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 319345.0,
      "end_time": 320912.0,
      "text": "on my Facebook page. (Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 320912.0,
      "end_time": 324169.0,
      "text": "And I actually untagged myself"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 324169.0,
      "end_time": 325633.0,
      "text": "first, then I picked up the"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 325633.0,
      "end_time": 326991.0,
      "text": "phone. I said, \"Mom, you will"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 326992.0,
      "end_time": 328104.0,
      "text": "never put a picture of me"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 328104.0,
      "end_time": 329393.0,
      "text": "in a bikini ever again.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 329393.0,
      "end_time": 332320.0,
      "text": "And she said, \"Why? You look"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 332321.0,
      "end_time": 334440.0,
      "text": "so cute, darling.\" I said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 334440.0,
      "end_time": 336233.0,
      "text": "\"You just don&#39;t understand.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 336233.0,
      "end_time": 338216.0,
      "text": "Maybe we are among the first"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 338216.0,
      "end_time": 339537.0,
      "text": "generation that really understands"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 339537.0,
      "end_time": 341727.0,
      "text": "this digital curating of ourselves."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 341728.0,
      "end_time": 343290.0,
      "text": "Maybe we are the first to even"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 343290.0,
      "end_time": 345528.0,
      "text": "actively record our lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 345528.0,
      "end_time": 347800.0,
      "text": "You know, whether you"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 347800.0,
      "end_time": 349233.0,
      "text": "agree with, you know, legacy"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 349233.0,
      "end_time": 351376.0,
      "text": "or not, we are actually leaving"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 351376.0,
      "end_time": 353729.0,
      "text": "behind digital traces all the time."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 353729.0,
      "end_time": 355784.0,
      "text": "So Netra and I really wanted"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 355784.0,
      "end_time": 357144.0,
      "text": "to use our 200-year plan"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 357144.0,
      "end_time": 359321.0,
      "text": "to curate this digital legacy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 359321.0,
      "end_time": 361160.0,
      "text": "and not only digital legacy"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 361160.0,
      "end_time": 362320.0,
      "text": "but we believe in curating"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 362320.0,
      "end_time": 364207.0,
      "text": "the legacy of my past"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 364208.0,
      "end_time": 365392.0,
      "text": "and future."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 365392.0,
      "end_time": 367225.0,
      "text": "How, you may ask?"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 367225.0,
      "end_time": 370793.0,
      "text": "Well, when I think of the future,"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 370793.0,
      "end_time": 372985.0,
      "text": "I never see myself moving forward"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 372985.0,
      "end_time": 375170.0,
      "text": "in time. I actually see time"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 375170.0,
      "end_time": 377890.0,
      "text": "moving backward towards me."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 377890.0,
      "end_time": 378489.0,
      "text": "I can actually visualize"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 378489.0,
      "end_time": 379840.0,
      "text": "my future approaching."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 379840.0,
      "end_time": 381953.0,
      "text": "I can dodge what I don&#39;t want"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 381953.0,
      "end_time": 383441.0,
      "text": "and pull in what I want."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 383441.0,
      "end_time": 384751.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s like a video game obstacle"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 384752.0,
      "end_time": 387238.0,
      "text": "course. And I&#39;ve gotten better and better"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 387238.0,
      "end_time": 389710.0,
      "text": "at doing this. Even when I make"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 389710.0,
      "end_time": 391104.0,
      "text": "a painting, I actually imagine"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 391104.0,
      "end_time": 393135.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m behind the painting,"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 393135.0,
      "end_time": 394318.0,
      "text": "it already exists, and"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 394318.0,
      "end_time": 395534.0,
      "text": "someone&#39;s looking at it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 395534.0,
      "end_time": 396623.0,
      "text": "and I see whether they&#39;re"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 396624.0,
      "end_time": 398245.0,
      "text": "feeling it from their gut."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 398245.0,
      "end_time": 399478.0,
      "text": "Are they feeling it from their"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 399478.0,
      "end_time": 402144.0,
      "text": "heart, or is it just a cerebral thing?"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 402144.0,
      "end_time": 404252.0,
      "text": "And it really informs my painting."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 404252.0,
      "end_time": 405443.0,
      "text": "Even when I do an art show,"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 405443.0,
      "end_time": 406467.0,
      "text": "I really think about, what should"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 406467.0,
      "end_time": 408190.0,
      "text": "people walk away with?"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 408190.0,
      "end_time": 410955.0,
      "text": "I remember when I was 19,"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 410955.0,
      "end_time": 413920.0,
      "text": "I did, I wanted to do my first"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 413920.0,
      "end_time": 416292.0,
      "text": "art exhibition, and I wanted the"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 416292.0,
      "end_time": 417698.0,
      "text": "whole world to know about it."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 417699.0,
      "end_time": 419147.0,
      "text": "I didn&#39;t know TED then,"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 419147.0,
      "end_time": 421147.0,
      "text": "but what I did was I closed"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 421148.0,
      "end_time": 422916.0,
      "text": "my eyes tight, and I started"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 422916.0,
      "end_time": 425188.0,
      "text": "dreaming. I could imagine people"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 425188.0,
      "end_time": 426731.0,
      "text": "coming in, dressed up, looking"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 426731.0,
      "end_time": 428764.0,
      "text": "beautiful, my paintings with all"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 428764.0,
      "end_time": 431475.0,
      "text": "the light, and in my visualization"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 431475.0,
      "end_time": 433331.0,
      "text": "I actually saw a very famous"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 433331.0,
      "end_time": 435499.0,
      "text": "actress launching my show,"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 435499.0,
      "end_time": 436996.0,
      "text": "giving credibility to me."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 436996.0,
      "end_time": 439580.0,
      "text": "And I woke up from my"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 439590.0,
      "end_time": 440316.0,
      "text": "visualization and I said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 440316.0,
      "end_time": 442510.0,
      "text": "who was that? I couldn&#39;t tell"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 442520.0,
      "end_time": 444291.0,
      "text": "if it was Shabana Azmi or Rekha,"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 444291.0,
      "end_time": 446500.0,
      "text": "two very famous Indian actresses,"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 446500.0,
      "end_time": 448347.0,
      "text": "like the Meryl Streeps of India."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 448347.0,
      "end_time": 450707.0,
      "text": "As it turned out, next morning"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 450707.0,
      "end_time": 452427.0,
      "text": "I wrote a letter to both of them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 452427.0,
      "end_time": 454380.0,
      "text": "and Shabana Azmi replied,"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 454380.0,
      "end_time": 456147.0,
      "text": "and came and launched"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 456147.0,
      "end_time": 459212.0,
      "text": "my very first show 12 years ago."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 459212.0,
      "end_time": 461444.0,
      "text": "And what a bang it started"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 461444.0,
      "end_time": 463244.0,
      "text": "my career with! You know,"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 463244.0,
      "end_time": 465660.0,
      "text": "when we think of time in this"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 465660.0,
      "end_time": 467979.0,
      "text": "way, we can curate not only the"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 467979.0,
      "end_time": 471496.0,
      "text": "future but also the past."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 471496.0,
      "end_time": 473700.0,
      "text": "This is a picture of my family,"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 473700.0,
      "end_time": 476323.0,
      "text": "and that is Netra, my wife."
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 476323.0,
      "end_time": 477955.0,
      "text": "She&#39;s the co-creator of my"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 477955.0,
      "end_time": 479436.0,
      "text": "200-year plan."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 479436.0,
      "end_time": 481474.0,
      "text": "Netra&#39;s a high school history"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 481475.0,
      "end_time": 483419.0,
      "text": "teacher. I love Netra,"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 483419.0,
      "end_time": 485236.0,
      "text": "but I hate history."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 485236.0,
      "end_time": 487147.0,
      "text": "I keep saying, \"Nets, you live"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 487148.0,
      "end_time": 488795.0,
      "text": "in the past while I&#39;ll create"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 488795.0,
      "end_time": 490796.0,
      "text": "the future, and when I&#39;m done,"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 490796.0,
      "end_time": 492292.0,
      "text": "you can study about it.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 492292.0,
      "end_time": 494251.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 494252.0,
      "end_time": 496251.0,
      "text": "She gave me an indulgent smile,"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 496251.0,
      "end_time": 498388.0,
      "text": "and as punishment, she said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 498388.0,
      "end_time": 500123.0,
      "text": "\"Tomorrow I&#39;m teaching a class"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 500123.0,
      "end_time": 502284.0,
      "text": "on Indian history, and you are"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 502284.0,
      "end_time": 503732.0,
      "text": "sitting in it, and I&#39;m grading you.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 503732.0,
      "end_time": 506750.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m like, \"Oh, God.\" I went."
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 506750.0,
      "end_time": 507378.0,
      "text": "I actually went and sat in"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 507379.0,
      "end_time": 509572.0,
      "text": "on her class. She started by"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 509572.0,
      "end_time": 511867.0,
      "text": "giving students primary source"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 511867.0,
      "end_time": 514482.0,
      "text": "documents from India, Pakistan,"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 514482.0,
      "end_time": 516731.0,
      "text": "from Britain, and I said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 516731.0,
      "end_time": 518875.0,
      "text": "\"Wow.\" Then she asked them to"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 518875.0,
      "end_time": 520827.0,
      "text": "separate fact from bias."
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 520827.0,
      "end_time": 523619.0,
      "text": "I said, \"Wow,\" again."
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 523619.0,
      "end_time": 526579.0,
      "text": "Then she said, \"Choose your"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 526579.0,
      "end_time": 529882.0,
      "text": "facts and biases and create an"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 529883.0,
      "end_time": 532162.0,
      "text": "image of your own story"
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 532162.0,
      "end_time": 533571.0,
      "text": "of dignity.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 533571.0,
      "end_time": 536826.0,
      "text": "History as an imaging tool?"
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 536826.0,
      "end_time": 538459.0,
      "text": "I was so inspired."
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 538459.0,
      "end_time": 539819.0,
      "text": "I went and created my own"
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 539819.0,
      "end_time": 541396.0,
      "text": "version of Indian history."
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 541396.0,
      "end_time": 543282.0,
      "text": "I actually included stories from"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 543283.0,
      "end_time": 544305.0,
      "text": "my grandmother."
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 544305.0,
      "end_time": 545464.0,
      "text": "She used to work for the"
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 545464.0,
      "end_time": 547320.0,
      "text": "telephone exchange, and she used"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 547320.0,
      "end_time": 548159.0,
      "text": "to actually overhear conversations"
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 548159.0,
      "end_time": 550328.0,
      "text": "between Nehru and Edwina Mountbatten."
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 550328.0,
      "end_time": 551904.0,
      "text": "And she used to hear all"
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 551904.0,
      "end_time": 553390.0,
      "text": "kinds of things she shouldn&#39;t"
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 553390.0,
      "end_time": 555545.0,
      "text": "have heard. But, you know,"
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 555545.0,
      "end_time": 556711.0,
      "text": "I include things like that."
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 556711.0,
      "end_time": 559505.0,
      "text": "This is my version of Indian history."
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 559505.0,
      "end_time": 563790.0,
      "text": "You know, if this"
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 563791.0,
      "end_time": 565905.0,
      "text": "is so, it occurred to me that"
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 565905.0,
      "end_time": 568127.0,
      "text": "maybe, just maybe, the primary"
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 568128.0,
      "end_time": 569567.0,
      "text": "objective of our brains"
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 569567.0,
      "end_time": 572607.0,
      "text": "is to serve our dignity."
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 572607.0,
      "end_time": 574615.0,
      "text": "Go tell Facebook to"
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 574615.0,
      "end_time": 575924.0,
      "text": "figure that out!"
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 575924.0,
      "end_time": 578544.0,
      "text": "Netra and I don&#39;t write our"
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 578544.0,
      "end_time": 580357.0,
      "text": "200-year plan for someone else"
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 580357.0,
      "end_time": 581381.0,
      "text": "to come and execute it"
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 581381.0,
      "end_time": 583524.0,
      "text": "in 150 years. Imagine receiving"
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 583524.0,
      "end_time": 585421.0,
      "text": "a parcel saying, from the past,"
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 585421.0,
      "end_time": 586784.0,
      "text": "okay now you&#39;re supposed to"
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 586784.0,
      "end_time": 587749.0,
      "text": "spend the rest of your life"
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 587749.0,
      "end_time": 589207.0,
      "text": "doing all of this. No."
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 589207.0,
      "end_time": 590854.0,
      "text": "We actually write it only"
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 590854.0,
      "end_time": 593344.0,
      "text": "to set our attitudes right."
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 593344.0,
      "end_time": 597184.0,
      "text": "You know, I used to believe"
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 597184.0,
      "end_time": 598584.0,
      "text": "that education is the most"
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 598584.0,
      "end_time": 600640.0,
      "text": "important tool to leave"
    },
    {
      "index": 294,
      "start_time": 600650.0,
      "end_time": 601522.0,
      "text": "a meaningful legacy."
    },
    {
      "index": 295,
      "start_time": 601522.0,
      "end_time": 603460.0,
      "text": "Education is great."
    },
    {
      "index": 296,
      "start_time": 603460.0,
      "end_time": 604695.0,
      "text": "It really teaches us who"
    },
    {
      "index": 297,
      "start_time": 604695.0,
      "end_time": 606310.0,
      "text": "we are, and helps us"
    },
    {
      "index": 298,
      "start_time": 606310.0,
      "end_time": 607349.0,
      "text": "contextualize ourselves"
    },
    {
      "index": 299,
      "start_time": 607350.0,
      "end_time": 609316.0,
      "text": "in the world, but it&#39;s really"
    },
    {
      "index": 300,
      "start_time": 609316.0,
      "end_time": 611375.0,
      "text": "my creativity that&#39;s taught me"
    },
    {
      "index": 301,
      "start_time": 611375.0,
      "end_time": 613152.0,
      "text": "that I can be much more"
    },
    {
      "index": 302,
      "start_time": 613152.0,
      "end_time": 615343.0,
      "text": "than what my education told me I am."
    },
    {
      "index": 303,
      "start_time": 615343.0,
      "end_time": 616796.0,
      "text": "I&#39;d like to make"
    },
    {
      "index": 304,
      "start_time": 616797.0,
      "end_time": 619127.0,
      "text": "the argument that creativity is"
    },
    {
      "index": 305,
      "start_time": 619127.0,
      "end_time": 621558.0,
      "text": "the most important tool we have."
    },
    {
      "index": 306,
      "start_time": 621558.0,
      "end_time": 623744.0,
      "text": "It lets us create who we are,"
    },
    {
      "index": 307,
      "start_time": 623744.0,
      "end_time": 625655.0,
      "text": "and curate what is to come."
    },
    {
      "index": 308,
      "start_time": 625655.0,
      "end_time": 628895.0,
      "text": "I like to think -- Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 309,
      "start_time": 628895.0,
      "end_time": 630470.0,
      "text": "I like to think of myself"
    },
    {
      "index": 310,
      "start_time": 630470.0,
      "end_time": 632806.0,
      "text": "as a storyteller, where my past"
    },
    {
      "index": 311,
      "start_time": 632806.0,
      "end_time": 635870.0,
      "text": "and my future are only stories,"
    },
    {
      "index": 312,
      "start_time": 635870.0,
      "end_time": 638159.0,
      "text": "my stories, waiting to be told"
    },
    {
      "index": 313,
      "start_time": 638159.0,
      "end_time": 640774.0,
      "text": "and retold. I hope all of you"
    },
    {
      "index": 314,
      "start_time": 640774.0,
      "end_time": 642718.0,
      "text": "one day get a chance to"
    },
    {
      "index": 315,
      "start_time": 642718.0,
      "end_time": 644545.0,
      "text": "share and write your own"
    },
    {
      "index": 316,
      "start_time": 644545.0,
      "end_time": 645910.0,
      "text": "200-year story."
    },
    {
      "index": 317,
      "start_time": 645910.0,
      "end_time": 646975.0,
      "text": "Thank you so much."
    },
    {
      "index": 318,
      "start_time": 646975.0,
      "end_time": 649158.0,
      "text": "Shukran! (Applause)"
    }
  ]
}